%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'fontFamily':'Calibri','fontSize':'18px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor ACC as 👤 Accountant
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BS as Billing Service
    participant IS as Integration Service
    participant CA as Chứng thư số CA
    participant EI as E-invoice Provider<br/>(Viettel/VNPT/Misa)
    participant TAX as Cơ quan thuế
    actor CUST as 👤 Khách hàng

    ACC->>FE: Mở Hóa đơn VAT → tạo từ đơn 123
    FE->>BS: POST /billing/vat/create { invoiceId, mst, ... }
    BS->>BS: Validate MST + tổng tiền + thuế
    alt Validation fail
        BS-->>FE: { code: 400, message }
        FE-->>ACC: ❌ Hiển thị lỗi
    else OK
        BS->>IS: requestSign(invoiceData)
        IS->>CA: Lấy chứng thư số (PFX/HSM)
        CA-->>IS: Chữ ký
        IS->>EI: POST /v2/invoice/issue with signature
        EI->>EI: Validate format
        EI->>TAX: Submit invoice
        TAX-->>EI: Mã tra cứu + URL PDF
        EI-->>IS: { lookupCode, pdfUrl }
        IS-->>BS: success
        BS->>BS: Save vat_invoice record
        BS->>CUST: Email PDF + link tra cứu
        BS-->>FE: { code: 0, lookupCode, pdfUrl }
        FE-->>ACC: ✅ Phát hành thành công
    end
